The Immunization search returned 0 results for patient S6540602 with CVX code 150 (influenza vaccine). This means no influenza vaccine record was found. Since there is no record of a prior vaccination, the condition "more than 365 days ago" cannot be determined from existing data, but the absence of any record implies no vaccine was given, so a new one should be ordered.

Now I will order the influenza vaccine for today (2024-01-09) using the MedicationRequest resource with the appropriate CVX code.

